Package: waldi
Title: Location-adjusted Wald statistics and confidence intervals
Version: 0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Ioannis", "Kosmidis", email = "ioannis.kosmidis@warwick.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	     person("Claudia", "Di Caterina", email = "dicaterina@stats.unipd.it", role = c("aut")))
Description: Provides methods for the computation of the location-adjusted Wald statistics derived in Di Caterina and Kosmidis <arXiv:1710.11217> for 'glm' and 'brglmFit' abjects, and corresponding methods for location-adjusted Wald confidence intervals.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.2)
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
